{"tid":201443,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有壞左既LG G3 / G4 想試下整？","createTime":"2017-04-14T17:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T03:03:34.000Z","uid":51134,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2271e0cc4a6543791a180e1377c2092059005d3","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"大家都知G3 G4 過熱死機問題一直令人詬病<br />\n<br />\n估計有d巴絲打部機可能係水貨／過左保而無拎去整<br />\n<br />\n小弟經過一輪google，發現死機問題可能係因為cpu過熱而導致脫焊<br />\n<br />\n救機方法暫時有兩種<br />\n1. reflow <br />\n2. 搵d野頂實粒u同底板<br />\n<br />\n如果你想試下救唔救得返，而你又唔介意既，不如拎比我試下<br />\n<br />\n講明先：<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 唔一定救得返</strong></span><br />\n2. 不收費，純粹想試下自己手勢（不過如果整得返，都歡迎你捐少少錢比任何慈善機構，以示支持）<br />\n<br />\n利申：剛剛用方法2 救左2部g3"},{"pid":"e341cd98c27181efe66d20e3c9928c2564de556b","tid":201443,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"5x bootloop 有無興趣整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2254639ac3a4d9bc9e06d2916a213be38440b8","tid":201443,"uid":34865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"有部g3韓水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n壞左兩年"},{"pid":"2db5099754181d6304a7c74681411ad37e64c9f3","tid":201443,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"有部g4<br />\n自已搵人整過一次<br />\n但係之後一唔叉電就死機reboot"},{"pid":"7dbfd7a56977a32e1d34c2cd553443078812e99a","tid":201443,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5x bootloop 有無興趣整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fb5677c4d676d5097c0a29fe3898d3bc09b494","tid":201443,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"過我個n5x bootloop 