rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個sim card槽係連埋micro sd</blockquote><br />\n係淘寶買sim卡槽連sd卡槽果組零件落黎自己換呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己整壞左g3卡槽都係淘落黎自己換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#adore<br />\n有神快拜<br />\n睇左段維修片，覺得個位好難焊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗焊架喎 就咁買件零件換咋喎"},{"pid":"5ad6e2be34ed238cb3fbe891aec5cfc0a20e1360","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T21:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lg g3早排開始壞<br />\n係咁重新開機，之後開始開機--&gt;出logo--&gt;重開無限loop<br />\n最後要叉住電先得<br />\n<br />\n係咪換咗粒電就冇事<br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路係<br />\n另一樣野你可以睇既, 比較開機前同後粒電個percentage<br />\n我粒壞電呢, 未開機前就30%, 開完機變左50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIf you find large difference, mostly likely your battery is dead."},{"pid":"64c1a82d50b8e51b4e2919c5fd0f0e9be9a4fdf0","tid":201443,"uid":61120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T21:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>g pro 2 壞左sim card位有冇得整<br />\n出面間間都唔整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry! 我冇專業架餐 整唔到<br />\nbtw 應該得大陸先肯幫你整<br />\n因為工序繁複 time cost太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsim card位自己整都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係咁易架葉師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個sim card槽係連埋micro sd</blockquote><br />\n係淘寶買sim卡槽連sd卡槽果組零件落黎自己換呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己整壞左g3卡槽都係淘落黎自己換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#adore<br />\n有神快拜<br />\n睇左段維修片，覺得個位好難焊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗焊架喎 就咁買件零件換咋喎</blockquote><br />\n對唔住 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇咗淘寶真係要焊<br />\n因為g3果件係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/055500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F055500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7ae21dd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"311e7209ca100e65fb0d30eabf6e92ad557d3a44","tid":201443,"uid":83692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T21:57:34.000Z","msg":"我部G3壞得好搞笑<br />\n叉實電就用到<br />\n一鬆電即刻無限重開機<br />\nChing知唔知係壞咩?"},{"pid":"5d982d125983e326dd4e36d3a44b571a8eb316c1","tid":201443,"uid":66679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:00:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dbc8141ef22a008cae028aa14fb5c595401e587","tid":201443,"uid":49222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:00:16.000Z","msg":"我部G3未洗機前會不斷重啓或者按幾下就黑屏，洗左機之後用用下會個mon會hold死個畫面之後就會自動熄機，大概係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f186f640f096aad83eb270d00a25a02547147a1","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n多謝師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我一定要叉住先得 一拔線又即刻開始無限loop<br />\n我試過見佢叉住都17%--&gt;56%--&gt;100%咁跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換完電部機就重生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當後備機用都唔錯"},{"pid":"5935c54a4fcffaee3a147cee2a58315802783b25","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我部G3壞得好搞笑<br />\n叉實電就用到<br />\n一鬆電即刻無限重開機<br />\nChing知唔知係壞咩?</blockquote><br />\n似死電"},{"pid":"dc65184662f034184048f1e38971d5ebcf5c2d2a","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我部G3未洗機前會不斷重啓或者按幾下就黑屏，洗左機之後用用下會個mon會hold死個畫面之後就會自動熄機，大概係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜曬, 你已中獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n粒cpu已脫焊(即係#0 個問題)"},{"pid":"af284eb7819af706d04667f8808315e64f23837f","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:10:18.000Z","msg":"頂<br />\n係咪真係有咁多人用G3呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時出街, 方圓三百里得我一個人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2495112640447738ac90cf3888adbc1d91bdfa96","tid":201443,"uid":61120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頂<br />\n係咪真係有咁多人用G3呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時出街, 方圓三百里得我一個人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲有G2 G3 G4擺左係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過G3壞電真係係好基本既事黎 <br />\n我都壞左2粒原廠電 依家用緊Momax"},{"pid":"ee54dbbbd0c211b1e5f1a9b1be510380cd1e102f","tid":201443,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:38:37.000Z","msg":"我都有部已死g3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係香港如果唔係爸打你拎去玩"},{"pid":"ef05e56170e5abe7cda15995d03c028d6e908a32","tid":201443,"uid":49222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我部G3未洗機前會不斷重啓或者按幾下就黑屏，洗左機之後用用下會個mon會hold死個畫面之後就會自動熄機，大概係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜曬, 你已中獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n粒cpu已脫焊(即係#0 個問題)</blockquote><br />\n原來咁就係脫焊，不過老母好似掉左部機，幫唔到爸打你練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e99a9550a1d95d47808b57ec211473ecc82073","tid":201443,"uid":30857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:54:11.000Z","msg":"有部g3 老豆整壞左sim卡slot 巴打攞唔攞去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前試過自己整 但解唔到桿"},{"pid":"945a46265becd7ec86ac973bb9a73702b3e57f24","tid":201443,"uid":23502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"g3 死cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c8eb3daec7c14e5cade727a50f7dd8e4e9392c","tid":201443,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"lg垃圾，整完咪轉個頭又壞，咪撚浪費時間啦"},{"pid":"1b0e68f62e897f319ac1a54345ef6f76eaf75b15","tid":201443,"uid":40354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:07:15.000Z","msg":"個wifi有時自動會長開，熄左又會自己開返<br />\n有時連到wifi又會自己斷線又再連無限loop<br />\n另外有時開機嗰時會自己過熱跟住又會無限reboot，有時reboot完係打唔出電話上唔到網，要我抆舊電出嚟一陣先至正常返<br />\n咁係咩問題？"},{"pid":"4277e797cf3b7d101227432979ad226ed4588b6c","tid":201443,"uid":62512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"我部g3 長期認為粒電係0%, 之後會reboot,  换過電都係咁， 咁仲有無得救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5205707fef0000adaa5bcb71954ee09658ccf3","tid":201443,"uid":34874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有部g3 老豆整壞左sim卡slot 巴打攞唔攞去玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前試過自己整 但解唔到桿</blockquote><br />\n其實好似都係關cpu事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc4a0c8d5bd4bacadabcffb9c2c05a3e365364e","tid":201443,"uid":83692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頂<br />\n係咪真係有咁多人用G3呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時出街, 方圓三百里得我一個人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲有G2 G3 G4擺左係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過G3壞電真係係好基本既事黎 <br />\n我都壞左2粒原廠電 依家用緊Momax</blockquote><br />\n啱呀,我部G3又係換完電冇耐又壞,索性換機算"},{"pid":"dfae5bb04b1bbd7f89bcc60d9a1d56cf4a03fa58","tid":201443,"uid":88495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"有部雙卡版g3<br />\n岩岩好過咗一年就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上上下網突然黑mon跟住就死咗機，差電同連電腦都完全冇反應<br />\n我又冇打機係刷下rom咁之嘛<br />\n咁係壞邊part？<br />\n諗住淘塊底板自己換/送淘寶整又唔知信唔信得過"},{"pid":"754350726c511c500bee1601383b08e74840312c","tid":201443,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"我死過G3 blue screen<br />\n拆左底板放入焗爐焗<br />\n醫返好一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7f303cf75b3a4f9a4263fbc04b38805aed05a2","tid":201443,"uid":55716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"壞左既v10得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ee62e17fe34f05b2a53c1fa47e63feefef41d5","tid":201443,"uid":44844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"部G4過完機場x 光機就收皮知唔知係咩死法?<br />\n年幾前已換一次底板"},{"pid":"2695b3f579e36fb27bb78f40d49027f58ddb02ff","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個wifi有時自動會長開，熄左又會自己開返<br />\n有時連到wifi又會自己斷線又再連無限loop<br />\n另外有時開機嗰時會自己過熱跟住又會無限reboot，有時reboot完係打唔出電話上唔到網，要我抆舊電出嚟一陣先至正常返<br />\n咁係咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n網上都有人share類似情況<br />\n估計都係cpu問題<br />\n佢放部機入焗爐焗10分鐘就冇事(即類似方法1)"},{"pid":"f7088a9f17b8ae9a31e058d04089c9d03341e757","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有部雙卡版g3<br />\n岩岩好過咗一年就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上上下網突然黑mon跟住就死咗機，差電同連電腦都完全冇反應<br />\n我又冇打機係刷下rom咁之嘛<br />\n咁係壞邊part？<br />\n諗住淘塊底板自己換/送淘寶整又唔知信唔信得過</blockquote><br />\nmost likely cpu<br />\n你可以試下好似條片咁整, 放個銀仔逼實粒U<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_fFZlg2Ydu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_fFZlg2Ydu8&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6a0ff3ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_fFZlg2Ydu8</a>"},{"pid":"e3fa4273306ad82f4365644009d0f06ea3aa291e","tid":201443,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:22:58.000Z","msg":"之前搵過LG為G4出咗個程式可以對付boot loop<br />\n大約係shut down其中啲有問題嘅核之類 詳情唔識咁多"},{"pid":"71b22bd69bd25ee21274e5da86fee10143d16b43","tid":201443,"uid":89272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱壞咗部g3,打打吓三國無隻突然藍畫面，有時開機入到桌面，幾秒又唔掂，換咗電都唔得，幫我reflow吓，唔該"},{"pid":"b7aa5ef5ea394f77105080d93fd51944e3271033","tid":201443,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有部g3 ,間中bootloop 同壞wifi ,自己整過幾次，過一排又壞返，係咪可以出手相救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你之前試過點整?<br />\n可以試下既, 但唔包整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nadd 唔到你wo 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104eecc503388b52354055cac1a4b41b15f06845","tid":201443,"uid":59840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:15:52.000Z","msg":"v10想唔想試下<br />\n<br />\n利申：拎過去整 救唔到"},{"pid":"017bc3994e2e395abb06d1f1fed74c3f62c3fc55","tid":201443,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有部G4 成日話 相機已停止 10次有1次又開得番<br />\n<br />\n關唔盟底板事</blockquote><br />\n可以係相機壞<br />\n或者係你某個相機app搞到相機crash左</blockquote><br />\nclean cache clean data<br />\nreboot<br />\nfactory reset<br />\n咩都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"6df90a4df892749585ffab05c6e720adbb52a3c9","tid":201443,"uid":71053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:25:18.000Z","msg":"我部g3 仲 run 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e130f7730fc89cfdc2579af31d4120b590d1562c","tid":201443,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"有部g3壞左成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682a9a38ffd507a3892aa300e2fb5304fa936a69","tid":201443,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"自己焗機焗好左真係shock左<br />\n其實咩原理？"},{"pid":"1711043edf44de36736da5081d93e7a3e55d89d2","tid":201443,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"樓主如果成功fix到5x bootloop可以講聲，唔介意俾返少少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36fb3fc22302b8e9e1cddb36d7ae40b9c11edfd7","tid":201443,"uid":56969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"有部會無啦啦閃mon嘅g3跟住就黑屏"},{"pid":"7373adf9dbae5ca774d1ba5de94747fec9e3e23b","tid":201443,"uid":106629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"LM 估唔到有咁多兄弟呢排壞同一款機 <br />\n我部GGG用左兩年半<br />\n第一年已經死電池 已換山寨電池繼續用<br />\n到上個月開始藍Mon 同bootloop<br />\n個mon識得都逐漸變黑又得 立即變黑又得 得左<br />\n即係一部機集曬以上咁多巴打所有毛病 :(<br />\n<br />\n真係無諗過拆底板出黎加熱可以救返架機<br />\n第一次烤完著得返我堅呆左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好景不常 一個禮拜又再藍mon<br />\n再拆出黎烤 兩三日又藍<br />\ne+唯有屢敗屢戰 但加熱救機法成功率依然維持100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1a15dc33cb894733f3654fd0b00bd86b14ca29","tid":201443,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"我都係屢敗屢戰 ，奈何佢一lag 機就會boot機，應該要換u先解決到"},{"pid":"e1643f1a57163b5e4658b571bc074035612eb846","tid":201443,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係屢敗屢戰 ，奈何佢一lag 機就會boot機，應該要換u先解決到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628ac9061476c4aa2a4f65e3dd5b0bb0a5b4b49c","tid":201443,"uid":106656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"我搵紙皮頂住塊底板半年啦 :0)<br />\n前日開始真係唔work<br />\n咩都睇唔到 仲要boot唔起<br />\n<br />\nreflow就冇試過<br />\n但試過搽散熱膏落去<br />\n有冇用唔知啦 但係機背果面嘅散熱膏冇凝固過<br />\n<br />\n等1+5/買V20算"},{"pid":"c433399cf6746a2317d189dd88b23f30b633ed31","tid":201443,"uid":106656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己焗機焗好左真係shock左<br />\n其實咩原理？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nReflow塊版其實係透過熱力將底板上面焊接位重新再「焊接」一次<br />\n好多人話work 但效力唔係永久<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前美國好多人幫人整電子嘢就係用 reflow soldering 呢個方法呃錢<br />\n之後就立法要加保養定咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57be9684a7057a12ac85ca2a676fbdcd4b9ed7a3","tid":201443,"uid":60242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"巴打 我部gpro2吾知點解一著機個相機鏡頭位就好熱 有冇解救方法"},{"pid":"8251c7b7cea98ebb3ac903e018db890d8c0c37c9","tid":201443,"uid":76009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾L G"},{"pid":"bea5d793b484dbbc1fe1b2c686d0093cb812dd77","tid":201443,"uid":30061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>g pro 2 壞左sim card位有冇得整<br />\n出面間間都唔整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry! 我冇專業架餐 整唔到<br />\nbtw 應該得大陸先肯幫你整<br />\n因為工序繁複 time cost太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsim card位自己整都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係咁易架葉師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個sim card槽係連埋micro sd</blockquote><br />\n其實唔太難，屋企人有幾部mon同sim卡加sd槽都係我換，最快嘅淘寶幾十蚊整電話個啲工具，sim卡槽好似都係十蚊到，再上網睇拆機片，搞掂！"},{"pid":"7dd17bd24db6b1c0f29d5c891610ae21b91a8a43","tid":201443,"uid":40354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個wifi有時自動會長開，熄左又會自己開返<br />\n有時連到wifi又會自己斷線又再連無限loop<br />\n另外有時開機嗰時會自己過熱跟住又會無限reboot，有時reboot完係打唔出電話上唔到網，要我抆舊電出嚟一陣先至正常返<br />\n咁係咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n網上都有人share類似情況<br />\n估計都係cpu問題<br />\n佢放部機入焗爐焗10分鐘就冇事(即類似方法1)</blockquote><br />\n底板受過潮係咪都可以照焗？"},{"pid":"fab31d05fb2cb74b082453a0359c827de04788c7","tid":201443,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家都知G3 G4 過熱死機問題一直令人詬病<br />\n<br />\n估計有d巴絲打部機可能係水貨／過左保而無拎去整<br />\n<br />\n小弟經過一輪google，發現死機問題可能係因為cpu過熱而導致脫焊<br />\n<br />\n救機方法暫時有兩種<br />\n1. reflow <br />\n2. 搵d野頂實粒u同底板<br />\n<br />\n如果你想試下救唔救得返，而你又唔介意既，不如拎比我試下<br />\n<br />\n講明先：<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 唔一定救得返</strong></span><br />\n2. 不收費，純粹想試下自己手勢（不過如果整得返，都歡迎你捐少少錢比任何慈善機構，以示支持）<br />\n<br />\n利申：剛剛用方法2 救左2部g3</blockquote><br />\n你個方法2應該幾日就打回原形<br />\n正確係要換cpu先真正整到</blockquote><br />\n方法2的確治標不治本，要越加越厚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 機主，已放棄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整嚟整定再壞，D人咁整都係為機入面data姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8eb3b8e4c0f52d26e624df62593a2c4af1e1341","tid":201443,"uid":103190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"我有部g4 應該都係死底版，點聯絡樓主？ 我add你tg話無username"},{"pid":"b8e1622787d0d028e5b89c68a252b8d374eb58af","tid":201443,"uid":83542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"G3 用用下就黑mon  開返得LG logo  閃左陣就漸漸變黑  有冇得整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c01a653765e230ec5abe42f8e3eb3315ae6978","tid":201443,"uid":43752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>G3 用用下就黑mon  開返得LG logo  閃左陣就漸漸變黑  有冇得整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣 不過我係update完"},{"pid":"5cbfce41ca12deb0faaf171283aa6aa2f18c17dd","tid":201443,"uid":93355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"有部g3港行<br />\n壞左一年<br />\ndetect唔到sim卡<br />\n相機爆玻璃<br />\n有無興趣？"},{"pid":"1be9f8de1c766ca63e5177803a8a9aef0a44c354","tid":201443,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"g2 刷上咗6.0<br />\n之後刷返落官方4.4個陣 磚咗<br />\n依家開機 入到個動畫畫面無限loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2725d4787a9bebb22be7b3a0abd3547ac95e109","tid":201443,"uid":51623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"有部G4卡咗喺LG logo...<br />\n巴打仲有冇興趣整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b75b827e88df9dee2a7b8ed77b6348af93d6016","tid":201443,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"g3個size 同外型好正 不過屌佢老母年半底板已燒"},